# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

Pylovara is a **rolling release project**.  
Only the **latest version** is supported at any time.

We strongly encourage all users to keep their installation up-to-date.

---

## Reporting a Vulnerability

If you discover a security issue, we appreciate your help in reporting it responsibly.

Please **open an issue** on GitHub or contact us via:

